OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,FStephen McCullagh has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto 31 years for the murder of Natalie
OL,8,FMcNally.
OL,10,FThe 36 year-old of Woodland Gardens,
OL,11,FLisburn, was found guilty by a jury at
OL,12,FBelfast Crown Court in March 2026.
OL,14,FNatalie McNally was 15 weeks pregnant
OL,15,Fwhen she was murdered at her home in
OL,16,FLurgan in December 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
