PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,FPassing sentence, trial judge Mr
OL,7,FJustice Kinney said McCullagh's
OL,8,Fculpability had been assessed as
OL,9,F"extremely high", describing the
OL,10,Fmurder as a "brutal and frenzied
OL,11,Fattack".
OL,13,FStephen McCullagh denied the murder,
OL,14,Fclaiming that he had been live-
OL,15,Fstreaming himself playing computer
OL,16,Fgames on his YouTube channel at the
OL,17,Ftime.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@PO]rD@MOUsD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,FPolice experts discovered the six-hour
OL,7,Fstream had actually been filmed four
OL,8,Fdays before, and broadcast as live on
OL,9,FDecember 18.
OL,11,FTrial judge MrJustice Kinney delivered
OL,12,Fthe sentence tariff at Belfast Crown
OL,13,FCourt on Wednesday.
OL,15,FHe said Stephen McCullagh's staged
OL,16,FYouTube live stream was an "integral"
OL,17,Fpart of his plan of murder her with
OL,18,Fthe staged live stream "carefully
OL,19,Fcurated" to "provide the defendant a
OL,20,Fcarefully-planned complete alibi to
OL,21,Fthe murder".
OL,26,@xD@\OUxD@eO]zD@XOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
