PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,FMr Justice Kinney also highlighted
OL,7,Fthat Stephen McCullagh spent time with
OL,8,Fthe McNally family in the aftermath of
OL,9,Fher death.
OL,11,FThe judge said McCullagh presented to
OL,12,Fthe family as "devastated, distraught
OL,13,Fand shocked".
OL,15,F"When he first arrived at the house on
OL,16,FChristmas Day, during Natalie's wake,
OL,17,Fthe family brought him in and
OL,18,Fcomforted him," the judge said.
OL,26,@tD@OOUuD@LO]wD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,F"They allowed him to spend extensive
OL,7,Ftime alone with Natalie, ostensibly to
OL,8,Fgrieve for her."
OL,10,FSetting the tariff, the judge said it
OL,11,Fwas "difficult to find words" to
OL,12,Fdescribe the "abhorrence" of his
OL,13,Fmurder of Natalie McNally.
OL,15,F"The defendant did not just kill
OL,16,FNatalie McNally, her unborn child also
OL,17,Fdied as a result of the murderous
OL,18,Fassault," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@PO]sD@EOUsD@]O]tD@NOUtD@YO]wD@
OL,26,AAOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,F"The defendant was fully aware that
OL,7,FNatalie was pregnant. He intended to
OL,8,Fkill her and he knew that her baby, at
OL,9,Fsuch an early stage of the pregnancy,
OL,10,Fwould have no chance of surviving the
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FStephen McCullagh sat in the dock
OL,14,Fwearing a grey short-sleeved T-shirt
OL,15,Fand tracksuit bottoms. The 36 year-old
OL,16,Fnodded when the sentence was handed
OL,17,Fdown.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,FCatherine Kierans, the Head of the
OL,7,FPublic Prosecution Service (PPS)
OL,8,FSerious Crime Unit said: "Natalie
OL,9,FMcNally was a much-loved young woman
OL,10,Fwhose life was full of promise.
OL,12,F"Stephen McCullagh, the father of her
OL,13,Funborn baby, violently and senselessly
OL,14,Ftook her life. Today marks the
OL,15,Fconclusion of proceedings to hold a
OL,16,Fcold and calculating murderer to
OL,17,Fjustice."
OL,26,@pD@ZOUyD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,FMs Kierans commended the bravery of
OL,7,FNatalie's loved ones including her
OL,8,Fparents and brothers, who attended
OL,9,Fevery court appearance.
OL,11,F"At the heart of this case are a
OL,12,Ffamily who have lost a loved one in
OL,13,Fthe most horrendous circumstances, and
OL,14,FI want to pay tribute to them. The
OL,15,Fdignified and respectful way in which
OL,16,Fthey engaged with the criminal justice
OL,17,Fsystem, while also dealing with
OL,18,Fdevastating loss and grief, is
OL,19,Fremarkable."
OL,26,@sD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,FMs Kierans described the case as a
OL,7,F'calculated' and 'premediated domestic
OL,8,Fmurder'.
OL,10,FShe added: "Natalie's murder was
OL,11,Funprecedented in the level of planning
OL,12,Fand sophistication. However, it is far
OL,13,Ffrom an isolated event. Violence
OL,14,Fagainst women and girls is a pervasive
OL,15,Fissue in this society that we all must
OL,16,Fwork together to tackle.
OL,26,@rD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,F"This case is another reminder of the
OL,7,Fhorrific scourge of violence against
OL,8,Fwomen and girls. Natalie's family have
OL,9,Fbravely spoken out, not only about her
OL,10,Fmurder, but this wider issue. Every
OL,11,Fvictim is one too many."
OL,13,FDetective Chief Inspector Neil
OL,14,FMcGuinness, the Senior Investigating
OL,15,FOfficer, said: "This was an attack
OL,16,Fthat sent shockwaves right across the
OL,17,Fcommunity. Not only was it
OL,18,Fdistressingly brutal in nature, it was
OL,19,Fmeticulously and coldly premeditated.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@POU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,F"McCullagh had devised an alibi,
OL,7,Fseemingly livestreaming for six hours
OL,8,Fon a social media platform at the time
OL,9,Fof Natalie's murder. In reality, he
OL,10,Fhad walked some distance from his home
OL,11,Fand taken a bus to Lurgan ` all the
OL,12,Fwhile concealing his appearance ` in
OL,13,Forder to carry out his attack.
OL,15,F"Thanks to the efforts and expertise
OL,16,Fof our Cyber Crime officers,
OL,17,Firrefutable evidence was obtained to
OL,18,Fshow that this footage had in fact
OL,19,Fbeen pre-recorded several days
OL,20,Fearlier."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector McGuinness
OL,7,Falso commended the McNally family for
OL,8,Ftheir "dignity and strength"
OL,9,Fthroughout the investigation and said
OL,10,Fhis thoughts remain with the family.
OL,12,FSpeaking outside the court, Natalie's
OL,13,Ffather Noel McNally said: "As my sons
OL,14,Fhave already said on the day of the
OL,15,Fverdict -
OL,17,F"Over the past three and a half years,
OL,18,Four family have been through
OL,19,Funimaginable pain and grief from the
OL,20,Floss of our beautiful Natalie.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,F"We would just like to thank everyone
OL,7,Fwho has helped us get to here today -
OL,8,Fall our family and friends, the whole
OL,9,Fcommunity of Lurgan, Craigavon and
OL,10,Fthroughout this country and beyond for
OL,11,Fall the kindness and support we have
OL,12,Freceived.
OL,14,F"We would also like to thank the PSNI
OL,15,Fand the prosecution service for
OL,16,Fgetting us to the conclusion here
OL,17,Ftoday.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1780488668
OL,3,CNatalie McNally's former partner
OL,4,Csentenced to 31 years for her murder
OL,6,F"Today is not a celebration of the
OL,7,Fsentence handed down as Bernadette, my
OL,8,Fboys and myself are serving a life
OL,9,Fsentence since the murder of our
OL,10,Fbeloved Natalie, but hopefully it will
OL,11,Fserve as a deterrent to help stop
OL,12,Fviolence against women and girls in
OL,13,Fthis country.
OL,15,FWith respect, we are now asking for
OL,16,Fsome privacy as we continue to grieve."
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/15
